column5: Timmins Ont , Sunday March23/09   12:00 am   Overnight  Sunday Temperature -22°C /Feels Like -32 Wind N 15km/h  Morning  Sunday Temperature -22°C /Feels Like -32 Wind N 15km/h  Afternoon  Sunday Temperature -15°C/ Feels Like -20   Wind N 15km/h   So good for the GroundHog and his shadow

Snow was just about gone here Friday morning, Friday evening we got 4 to 6 inches and colder temps with it. Supposed to be back in the 50`s next week though. April 15th tax day here usually means an end to the snow also.
I dunno what y'all folks are going on about... I'm working on my tan!
Minus 16 here last night the snow is not melting at all  Glen send us pics of warm spring.
